Title: Add Host/Service state summary dashlet
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1631798601
Edition: cee
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

New dashlet that shows a summary of Services/Hosts
in a certain state.

It displays the amount of Services/Hosts in the selected
state and the total amount of Services/Hosts within the
configured context.
